    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Follow up upcoming appointments with Google Drive and Slack automatically\n\n**Pattern:** Reminders & Follow-ups · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nFollow up upcoming appointments with Google Drive and Slack automatically. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual deal updates is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Slot Free? → Record Booking → Send Confirmation (Slack) → Hold Until Reminder Time → Send Reminder (Slack) → Align Field Names → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to reminders & follow-ups without manual effort\n- Anyone automating deal updates in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Responds in seconds\n- Scales without extra headcount\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "339dd51f-8308-7ed3-f0fd-9da8176e94cf",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.",
        "width": 360,
        "height": 260,
        "color": 1
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -230,
        -260
      ],
      "id": "c62e0e85-237c-b669-5315-578cca0cff89",
      "name": "⏱ Rate limiting"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your deal updates process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.",
        "width": 360,
        "height": 260,
